p23
aVThis is a child that's born, young girl.
p24
aV"Day of life zero," we call it,
p25
aVthe first day of life, just born into the world.
p26
aVAnd just as she's being born,
p27
aVwe notice very quickly that she is deteriorating.
p28
aVHer heart rate is going up, her blood pressure is going down,
p29
aVshe's breathing very, very fast.
p30
aVAnd the reason for this is displayed in this chest X-ray.
