aa(lp44
VThe fix for this problem
p45
aVis to take this child immediately to the operating room,
p46
aVbring those intestines back into the abdomen,
p47
aVlet the lungs expand
p48
aVand allow this child to breathe again.
p49
aVBut before she can go to the operating room,
p50
aVshe must get whisked away to the ICU, where I work.
p51
aVI work with surgical teams.
p52
aVWe gather around her,
p53
aVand we place this child on heart-lung bypass.
p54
aVWe put her to sleep,
p55
aVwe make a tiny little incision in the neck,
p56
aVwe place catheters into the major vessels of the neck \u2014
p57
aVand I can tell you that these vessels are about the size of a pen,
p58
aVthe tip of a pen \u2014
p59
aVand then we have blood drawn from the body,
p60
aVwe bring it through a machine, it gets oxygenated,
